data.name: textBox5.Text
data.value:
v1.4.0.0 -We changed UI, color and icon. -We added "Program" search in Scan feature. -We added system commands to XShort Run. +To use tab function with system commands, a # character must be placed at first. -We added Index Search, Auto-Index and Build Index feature. -We added "Don't load main list at startup" option and "Reload data button". -We fixed bugs and improved user experience.
v1.2.2.1 -Fixed log bug. -Fixed bug which cannot open some applications/games. -Added Auto option in Skin setting. -Added "Open at Windows startup" function. -Added option to change hotkey of XShort Run. -Improved Scan folder speed, added scan file name option.
v1.2.2.0 -Fixed bugs. Improved About tab. -Changed the way to: add, edit shortcuts. Added log, undo. -Added more options in Scan folder. Now you can sort the list. -Added multi-call, use "|" between call name. Support tab function. -Added translate function, use ">". Ex: monster>en|vi or monster>. Requires internet. -Fixed bug and improved parameter run. Now you can use tab function. Does not support multi-call.

data.name: textBox2.Text
data.value: Shortcut Keys: Ctrl + Shift + A to add new application/file Ctrl + Shift + D to add new directory Ctrl + Shift + C to add new URL Ctrl + Shift+ S to save shortcuts --------------------------- Ctrl + A to open About Ctrl + S to open Settings Ctrl + X to open Build Index Ctrl + I to import data Ctrl + E to export data Ctrl + F to scan folder Ctrl + U to check for updates Ctrl + H to go to homepage Ctrl + L to open log Alt + F4 to exit Alt + Q to minimize and hide --------------------------- Alt + A to show run box (you can change this) Ctrl + Tab to show main window --------------------------- Tab to use tab function Control to extract call name to path and copy to clipboard --------------------------- Use + between call names to activate multi-call Use > after a word to activate translate function
